  Task 6: Replace Issue Names (Standardization) 
• Replace all:  
o "rude behavior" → "rude_behavior"  
o "late arrival" → "late_arrival"  

Code:
# Traditional loop
Standardized_Rides = [] #  empty list create chesukovali
for Ride in Rides:
   # Step 1: Replace "rude behavior" → "rude_behavior"
   Ride = Ride.replace("rude behavior", "rude_behavior")

   # Step 2: Replace "late arrival" → "late_arrival"
   Ride = Ride.replace("late arrival", "late_arrival")

   # Step 3: Append standardized ride into list
   Standardized_Rides.append(Ride)

for i, Ride in enumerate(Standardized_Rides, start=1):
  print(f"Ride {i} : {Ride}")

Output:
Ride 1 : ride101-ramesh-late_arrival-bangalore
Ride 2 : ride102-suresh-rude_behavior-hyderabad
Ride 3 : ride103-mahesh-late_arrival-bangalore



